{"tid":234200,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"【叫咗你裝Linux】港珠澳大橋電腦遭黑客加密勒索","createTime":"2017-05-08T06:05:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-08T11:40:18.000Z","uid":11001,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fad381866f5cff10d689ece4c30eb1d89d99bd4e","tid":234200,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T06:05:38.000Z","msg":"港珠澳大橋工程又出事，路政署向《立場新聞》證實，大橋地盤辦公室的電腦伺服器遭加密勒索。不過署方強調工人資料未有受影響，事件亦沒無影響工程進度。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">路政署發言人證實，今年3月2日路政署接獲工程合約編號HY/2011/09的駐工地工程人員通知，指駐工地工程人員寫字樓內的伺服器遭勒索軟件（Ransomware）攻擊，伺服器內的部份檔案遭加密勒索。</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 經發現後，駐工地工程人員已即時切斷有關伺服器的網絡連線，並向警方求助。<br />\n<br />\n路政署指，據顧問公司的回覆，駐工地工程人員的個人資料及由承建商呈交的工人資料，並沒有儲存於受勒索軟件攻擊的伺服器內，因此有關資料未有受影響。 路政署已要求駐工地工程人員及承建商，更新其寫字樓內所有電腦的網絡保安軟件，以加強網絡保安，有關事件並沒有影響該合約的工程進度。 <br />\n<br />\n《東方日報》今日頭版報道指，3月初工程顧問公司奧雅納的工程人員，於粵港分界線至觀景山的一段香港接線地盤，發現伺服器遭黑客以加密勒索軟件攻擊。伺服器內有大量工程相關的檔案，包括工程顧問批核的施工物料種類及數量、工程進度報表、工程草圖等。有關公司報警求助後雖解除「挾持」，但部分檔案最終仍被黑客刪除。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E6%B8%AF%E7%8F%A0%E6%BE%B3%E5%A4%A7%E6%A9%8B%E9%9B%BB%E8%85%A6%E9%81%AD%E9%BB%91%E5%AE%A2%E5%8A%A0%E5%AF%86%E5%8B%92%E7%B4%A2-%E8%B7%AF%E6%94%BF%E7%BD%B2-%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E9%80%B2%E5%BA%A6%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%97%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%258F%25A0%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25A9%258B%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%2585%25A6%25E9%2581%25AD%25E9%25BB%2591%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%25AF%2586%25E5%258B%2592%25E7%25B4%25A2-%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E6%2594%25BF%25E7%25BD%25B2-%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E7%25A8%258B%25E9%2580%25B2%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E9%259F%25BF%2F&d=sZqGLlkYYIxatccyfr7NWEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=8b549249\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%258F%25A0%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25A9%258B%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%2585%25A6%25E9%2581%25AD%25E9%25BB%2591%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%25AF%2586%25E5%258B%2592%25E7%25B4%25A2-%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E6%2594%25BF%25E7%25BD%25B2-%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E7%25A8%258B%25E9%2580%25B2%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E9%259F%25BF%2F&h=5cc3e6b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E6%B8%AF%E7%8F%A0%E6%BE%B3%E5%A4%A7%E6%A9%8B%E9%9B%BB%E8%85%A6%E9%81%AD%E9%BB%91%E5%AE%A2%E5%8A%A0%E5%AF%86%E5%8B%92%E7%B4%A2-%E8%B7%AF%E6%94%BF%E7%BD%B2-%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E9%80%B2%E5%BA%A6%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%97%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF/</a>"},{"pid":"626fd15d00d32dd8ae4bb8e6c386d5a3e1ba9430","tid":234200,"uid":73231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T06:47:08.000Z","msg":"屈落黑客到<br />\n肯定啲文件本身唔見得光"},{"pid":"3c5a3794c7b3c13123238d9b9a5a4f4295623437","tid":234200,"uid":36551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T06:54:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屈落黑客到<br />\n肯定啲文件本身唔見得光</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5c9026ffabb2287e3206867fcaeb2b97213dd17","tid":234200,"uid":60249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T07:51:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"03be84e88686345c4100f3d8a3d0e1e2774cfe00","tid":234200,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T08:03:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屈落黑客到<br />\n肯定啲文件本身唔見得光</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4664879a8603a6904ae2b1324fdac294cd980c6f","tid":234200,"uid":35216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T08:21:11.000Z","msg